Package com.serezk4.database.mapper

package com.serezk4.database.mapper
Package for mapping entities to data transfer objects (DTOs) and vice versa.

The mapper package defines interfaces and classes for converting database entities into DTOs and vice versa. This abstraction simplifies data transformation logic and ensures consistency across layers.

Main components:

  • Mapper: Generic interface for mapping logic.
  • UserMapper: Maps User to UserDto.
